## Objective

Replace the tab strip in `QuestionPrompt` with sequential Back/Next buttons and a step indicator for multi-question flows. This creates a simpler, more focused sequential navigation.

## Current Code

In `apps/client/src/layers/features/chat/ui/QuestionPrompt.tsx`, the multi-question section (around line 396):

```tsx
<Tabs value={activeTab} onValueChange={setActiveTab}>
  <TabsList className="mb-3 h-auto flex-wrap gap-1.5 bg-transparent p-0">
